<body>
    <p style="color:rgb(111, 0, 255)">Seasons are periods of the year with distinct weather conditions and day lengths.</p>

    <p style="color:rgb(183, 0, 255)">four seasons — winter, spring, summer, autumn — can vary significantly in characteristics and can prompt changes in the world around them. Here, we explore these four seasons in more detail. 
</p>

    <p> Attributes of the seasons may vary by location, but there are still broad definitions that cross most of the boundaries.

